# corvin_license/pubkey.pem is INTENTIONALLY committed — see ADR-0017 §III.
# It is the embedded pinned trust anchor; the entire license-gate security
# model depends on it living in the source tree. Only the corresponding
# private key (~/.corvin/maintainer-keys/maintainer-priv.pem) stays off-tree.
